{"tid":1580553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［熱烈慶賀］《大公報》僭建招牌已拆卸　白帆布遮蓋外牆","createTime":"2019-09-19T06:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T09:34:39.000Z","uid":68738,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"58a804ff1da7095ee3df070bf9c96a523d4a51e1","tid":1580553,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190919/photo/bkn-20190919115659882-0919_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190919121732\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190919%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190919115659882-0919_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190919121732&h=35af4c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位於灣仔軒尼詩道的《大公報》招牌早前被揭發為僭建物，屋宇署於7月下旬下令清拆，要求業主60天內還原。東網記者今早(19日)到場視察發現招牌已被拆卸，相關位置已築起棚架及白色帆布遮蓋。<br />\n<br />\n該灰底紅字招牌原座落於灣仔軒尼詩道國華大廈《大公報》報社舊址。屋宇署表示，根據紀錄，附建於上址2至3樓，面向軒尼詩道外牆裝有發光二極體(LED)展示系統的招牌，是根據《建築物條例》規定，獲該署批准豎設，但在該招牌下方1樓外牆一個面積約為12米寬、2米高的招牌，豎設前未獲屋宇署批准，屬違例招牌但並沒有明顯危險。<br />\n<br />\n由於該招牌面積屬於屋宇署針對大型違例招牌執法行動的目標招牌，該署根據《建築物條例》第24條向有關人士發出清拆令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190919/mobile/bkn-20190919115659882-0919_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190919%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190919115659882-0919_00822_001.html&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5b7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=86c7f116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190919/mobile/bkn-20190919115659882-0919_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7c255dec69d759704be5cf3379934fcf706f8286","tid":1580553,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:31:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https